data.title: Metal Mulisha Exhaust - Jeep JK by Gibson Performance
data.tags: Metal Mulisha Exhaust, Gibson Performance, Jeep Wrangker JK, Jeep exhaust, Wrangler exhaust
data.description:
Metal Mulisha Exhaust by Gibson Performance hits the market hard with all new sound and style for Jeep JK owners, '07-present 2 & 4 door models.  Each Black Ceramic coated system bumps up the decibels with a throaty tone, and features Metal Mulisha Stainless Steel Skull badges wrapped around HUGE dual 5" rear-exit exhaust tips! All Metal Mulisha Exhaust exhaust systems are manufactured for hassle-free installation, Made in the U.S.A, and finished with Gibson Performance's commitment to their customer by including a Lifetime Limited Warranty. 

Brian Deegan, Metal Mulisha's founder and decorated X-Games & multi-talented racing champion commented, "The Metal Mulisha Exhaust brings the motor to life and makes it fun to drive! That's why all my vehicles and race trucks run the Metal Mulisha Exhaust!" 

Part #60-0023
- '07-'11 3.8L Jeep JK 2/4 Door
- 2012  3.6L Jeep JK 2/4 Door

data.title: Gibson Exhaust on 2015 Mustang GT 5.0L with Dyno Run
data.tags: Gibson Performance Exhaust, Gibson Exhaust Systems, 2015 Ford Mustang GT, dyno, gibson 619013
data.description:
Stainless System, Part # 619013  //  Elite Black Ceramic, Part # 619013-B

Dyno Graph:
http://gibsonperformance.com/products/retail_prod_annoucement.php?product_number=619013-B

Dyno tested to:
32 hp gain @ 6500 rpm
34 ft-lbs gain @ 4000 rpm

Gibson Performance introduces a new Dual Exhaust system to give the redesigned 6th Generation 2015 Ford Mustang 5.0 steed an extra shot of American-Made power, combined with an aggressive sound that lets others know to take notice.
  
The complete Dual 3” Stainless Steel X Pipe and trusted, power-proven SuperFlow mufflers with integrated CFT technology will create symphony under the chassis, as they work in tune to push any driver deeper into their seat.  With each rap of the throttle, the throaty sound exiting from the Dual 4.5” Intercooled Stainless Tips will work to alter their ego from Office Clerk to Road Warrior.

Choosing between Raw Stainless or Elite Black Ceramic finishes could take longer than installing this Gibson Direct-Fit bolt-on exhaust system, allowing more time to burn fuel and lay rubber. To top it off, the Gibson craftsmen in Corona, California will back this American-Made exhaust system with a Lifetime Limited Warranty to ensure satisfaction is guaranteed.

data.title: 2013 Ford F-350 CrewCab 6.2L with Gibson Dual Extreme Exhaust
data.tags: Gibson Exhaust Systems, Gibson Performance Exhaust, cat back exhaust, Ford F-250, F250, Ford F-350, F350 dual exhaust, gibson
data.description:
Part # 9125 Aluminized (Also available in Stainless #69125)
11-15 Ford F250/F350 Super duty Crew Cab, Long Bed 6.2L 2/4wd

Part # 9118 Aluminized (Also available in Stainless #69118)
11-15 Ford F250/F350 Super duty Crew Cab, Short Bed 6.2L 2/4wd

For the extremist who wants to take their truck to the next level, this dual bolt-on Cat back system is for you. This system exists behind the rear tires at an aggressive angle with a powerful exhaust tone. You will gain bold street looks with powerful dyno tuned and tested street performance gains. You can expect to experience gains on average of 15-20 horsepower. Gibson muffler provides a mean performance sound and complemented with polished Stainless Tip. Easy bolt-on installation. No welding required. Backed by a Lifetime Limited Warranty. If you want Extreme, this system is it.

– 2.50-in. aluminized mandrel bent tubing.
– Gibson Muffler features a baffled & chambered design, no internal packing, powerful deep tone. 7" x 7" x 24" Round Muffler
– 4in. Polished T304 Stainless Rolled Slash- Cut Tip.
– Exits Behind Each Rear Tire.
– Includes all hardware and factory style hangers for easy bolt on installation.
– Slip Connection to Converter
– Lifetime Limited Warranty
